      %td
        =r.energy
        vs
        =r.strength

%p The important thing to realize is that whatever your cycle, it affects all four realms of behavior equally. That is, you cannot be Up in the Physical realm and Down in the Mental realm. If you are Up, then you are Up in <em>all four</em> realms.
%p Your BipolarType is based on which realms are easiest for you to <em>act</em> Up or Down in, when you are <em>not</em> Up or Down. That is, can you #{Realm.first.up} when you are Down? Can you <em>not</em> #{Realm.first.up} when you are Up? Can you #{Realm.first.down} when you are Up? Can you <em>not</em> #{Realm.first.down} when you are Down?

